43:36.166 --> 43:37.291
[all]
♪ Baby, baby ♪

43:37.291 --> 43:40.041
♪ Rock me gently ♪

43:40.041 --> 43:41.375
♪ Rock me slowly ♪

43:41.375 --> 43:44.083
♪ Take it easy ♪

43:44.083 --> 43:45.542
♪ Don't you know ♪

43:45.542 --> 43:47.583
♪ That I have never been ♪

43:47.583 --> 43:50.417
♪ Loved like this before? ♪

43:50.417 --> 43:54.917
♪ music broods ♪

43:54.917 --> 43:57.583
♪♪♪

43:57.583 --> 43:59.417
[Andy Kim]
♪ Oh, my darling ♪

43:59.417 --> 44:02.125
♪ Oh, my baby ♪

44:02.125 --> 44:06.291
♪ You got the moves
that drive me crazy ♪

44:06.291 --> 44:08.291
♪ ominous music ♪

44:08.291 --> 44:14.208
♪♪♪

44:24.250 --> 44:25.792
Ray.

44:25.792 --> 44:27.959
[rain pattering]

44:33.792 --> 44:35.458
What's going on?

44:35.458 --> 44:37.959
Sit down.

44:46.250 --> 44:49.834
What's up, Ter?

44:49.834 --> 44:51.917
I got something to tell you.

44:57.000 --> 44:59.500
Ab--

44:59.500 --> 45:02.500
Abby--

45:02.500 --> 45:04.500
What?

45:12.166 --> 45:13.750
Abby was right.

45:13.750 --> 45:16.208
I shouldn't have lied.

45:16.208 --> 45:17.917
Lied about what?

45:22.125 --> 45:23.834
Ah.

45:23.834 --> 45:27.125
You know, it's over
between me and Maureen.

45:27.125 --> 45:28.041
What are you talking about?

45:28.041 --> 45:31.375
Her brother found out
about Nevada.

45:31.375 --> 45:33.917
So?

45:33.917 --> 45:35.291
[sniffles]

45:35.291 --> 45:37.291
You made a mistake, Ter.
It happens.

45:37.291 --> 45:38.542
Take it.

45:38.542 --> 45:39.625
No.

45:39.625 --> 45:41.083
Abby wanted her to have it.

45:41.083 --> 45:45.041
[sniffles]
Not like this, Ray.

45:45.041 --> 45:47.875
Not like this.

45:55.583 --> 45:58.542
[people]
chattering in Spanish

45:58.542 --> 46:02.125
[thunder rumbles]

46:03.959 --> 46:05.875
I'm sorry, babe.

46:05.875 --> 46:07.917
We'll be fine.

46:07.917 --> 46:10.875
You still have your job
at Ray's office.

46:10.875 --> 46:14.709
I can stay home
and look after Maria.

46:15.792 --> 46:17.166
You go.

46:17.166 --> 46:19.750
You go on the tour.

46:19.750 --> 46:22.875
- Yeah, but what about--
- Go.

46:22.875 --> 46:25.792
I'll stay home with Maria,
all right?

46:25.792 --> 46:29.625
At least that's
one thing I ain't so bad at.

46:29.625 --> 46:33.417
You ain't so bad
at a lot of things, Brendan.

46:35.208 --> 46:38.125
[thunder rumbles]

46:40.125 --> 46:42.959
[Mickey] Michael's got
his semiautomatic in one hand

46:42.959 --> 46:44.375
and the bag of cash

46:44.375 --> 46:46.542
for his daughter's heart
in the other.

46:46.542 --> 46:47.583
"Drop the gun," says the cop.

46:47.583 --> 46:50.417
"Drop the gun."

46:50.417 --> 46:51.750
Michael whispers to himself,

46:51.750 --> 46:55.125
"I can't let you down, Angela."

46:55.125 --> 46:57.000
"Drop the fucking gun."

46:57.000 --> 46:58.709
Michael drops the money

46:58.709 --> 47:00.959
and keeps his gun
pointing at the cops,

47:00.959 --> 47:03.125
knowing they'll shoot.

47:03.125 --> 47:05.083
"Not in my heart,"

47:05.083 --> 47:06.709
says Michael moving forward.

47:06.709 --> 47:09.000
"Whatever you do,
not in my heart.

47:09.000 --> 47:09.792
You hear me?

47:09.792 --> 47:13.000
My little girl needs my heart."

47:13.000 --> 47:16.208
[imitates crying]

47:16.208 --> 47:18.166
[exhales deeply]

47:21.625 --> 47:23.083
You startled me.

47:31.166 --> 47:34.750
Did you tell Terry
I got the boutonnieres?

47:34.750 --> 47:37.000
They're in the fridge.

47:47.417 --> 47:51.417
[Bridget sobbing]

47:51.417 --> 47:53.458
♪ soft music ♪

47:53.458 --> 47:59.375
♪♪♪

48:11.375 --> 48:14.291
[sobbing continues]

48:17.041 --> 48:21.208
♪♪♪

48:25.041 --> 48:27.208
[sobbing continues]

48:32.083 --> 48:32.625
[Bridget] Dad.

48:32.625 --> 48:36.542
What happened?

48:38.917 --> 48:41.834
[Bridget sobbing]

48:48.500 --> 48:50.583
[rain pattering]

48:50.583 --> 48:54.291
[music fades]

48:54.291 --> 48:57.208
[thunder rumbles]

49:41.291 --> 49:44.750
[Mickey] Now the camera
is close up, on gurney wheels

49:44.750 --> 49:45.959
moving fast.

49:45.959 --> 49:47.291
And the nurse says,

49:47.291 --> 49:49.375
"Angela, we have a match.

49:49.375 --> 49:52.000
You're gonna live.
You're gonna live."

49:52.000 --> 49:53.750
And off Angela's face,

49:53.750 --> 49:56.542
not knowing
she's getting Michael's heart,

49:56.542 --> 49:59.417
we see finally a ray of hope.

49:59.417 --> 50:03.083
Hope.

50:06.625 --> 50:08.875
It's a triumph.

50:08.875 --> 50:11.208
It's a fucking triumph.

50:11.208 --> 50:13.333
[exhales deeply]

50:20.333 --> 50:23.250
[exhales deeply]

50:55.417 --> 50:59.709
She was the brightest star
in the sky.

51:02.083 --> 51:04.917
You sleep, kid.

51:04.917 --> 51:06.542
