"Madman Across the Water" ♪

51:06.542 --> 51:09.375
♪ I can see ♪

51:09.375 --> 51:12.458
♪ Very well ♪

51:12.458 --> 51:14.000
♪ There's a boat on the reef ♪

51:14.000 --> 51:16.959
♪ With a broken back ♪

51:16.959 --> 51:21.000
♪ And I can see it very well ♪

51:21.000 --> 51:25.917
♪♪♪

51:25.917 --> 51:28.041
♪ There's a joke ♪

51:28.041 --> 51:31.208
♪ And I know it very well ♪

51:31.208 --> 51:32.250
♪♪♪

51:32.250 --> 51:35.583
♪ It's one of those
that I told you ♪

51:35.583 --> 51:38.375
♪ Long ago ♪

51:38.375 --> 51:39.792
♪ Take my word,
I'm a madman ♪

51:39.792 --> 51:43.125
♪ Don't you know? ♪

51:43.125 --> 51:47.083
♪♪♪

51:47.083 --> 51:48.959
♪ Once a fool ♪

51:48.959 --> 51:50.875
♪ Had a good part ♪

51:50.875 --> 51:54.500
♪ In the play ♪

51:54.500 --> 51:56.291
♪ If it's so, would I still ♪

51:56.291 --> 51:59.250
♪ Be here today? ♪

51:59.250 --> 52:00.750
♪ It's quite peculiar ♪

52:00.750 --> 52:04.792
♪ In a funny sort of way ♪

52:04.792 --> 52:06.250
♪ They think it's very funny ♪

52:06.250 --> 52:10.083
♪ Everything I say ♪

52:10.083 --> 52:11.458
♪♪♪

52:11.458 --> 52:13.166
♪ Well, get a load of him ♪

52:13.166 --> 52:16.667
♪ He's so insane ♪

52:16.667 --> 52:20.041
♪ You better get
your coat, dear ♪

52:20.041 --> 52:24.583
♪ It looks like rain ♪

52:24.583 --> 52:29.250
♪ We'll come again
next Thursday afternoon ♪

52:29.250 --> 52:32.000
♪♪♪

52:32.000 --> 52:36.125
♪ The in-laws hope
they'll see you very soon ♪

52:36.125 --> 52:39.125
♪♪♪

52:39.125 --> 52:41.834
♪ But is it in your conscience ♪

52:41.834 --> 52:44.166
♪ That you're after ♪

52:44.166 --> 52:46.458
♪♪♪

52:46.458 --> 52:51.417
♪ Another glimpse of
the madman across the water? ♪

